<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَالثَّانِي:</span> لَا يَبْطُلُ؛ لأَنَّ الْمَفْهُومَ كَالنَّصِ فِي إفَادَةِ الْحُكْمِ، فَيَصِيرُ فِي الْمَسْأَلةِ قَوْلَانِ إِنْ كَانَا عَامَّيْنِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>كَقَوْلِهِ فِي الْأَبِ وَالْأَخِ، لَمَّا سُئِلَ عَنْ عِتْقِ الْأَبِ بِالشِّرَاءِ؟<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">فَقَال:</span> <span class="c1">"يُعْتَقُ"</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَعَنْ <span class="c4">[عِتْقِ]</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> الأْخ بِهِ؟<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">فَقَال:</span> <span class="c1">"يُعْتَقُ"</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">فَمَفْهُومُ الْأَوَّلَةِ:</span> أَنَّ الْأَخَ لَا يُعْتَقُ،<span class="c5"> وَلَفْظُ الثَّانِيَةِ:</span> أَنهُ يُعْتَقُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">فَإِنْ قُلْنَا:</span> <span class="c1">" <span class="c4">[إِنَّ]</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> الْمَفْهُومَ يَبْطُلُ بِالْمَنْطُوقِ"</span>؛ كَانَتِ الْمَسْأَلةُ رِوَايَة وَاحِدَةً،<span class="c5"> وَإِلَا صَارَ فِي الْأَخِ رِوَايَتَانِ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">إِحْدَاهُمَا:</span> بِنَصِّهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وَالأُخْرَى:</span> بِنَقْلٍ وَتَخْرِيجٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>* * *<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) من (أ).<br>(٢) الرواية ذكرها ابن حامد في (تهذيب الأجوبة): ٢/ ٨٢٩.<br>(٣) من (أ).</p> </div>